                </h2>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 bloc landing-page-section4-first-bloc">
                    <div class="landing-page-section4-bloc">
                        <div class="landing-page-section4-bloc-image">
                            <img class="landing-page-section4-img" src="/images/homePage/beevup-img-man.png" alt="">
